<p>
	John and Dave&#8230; Dave and John&#8230; are here, helping you solve all your Mac problems by answering your questions, sharing tips, finding Cool Stuff (and sharing that, too), and much, much more. Topics covered today include making Photo Stream friendlier, managing your clones (both local and network), troubleshooting FireWire disks, and fixing that pesky menu bar clock when it stops ticking. All this and more on this week&#39;s episode of Mac Geek Gab! Download today and enjoy!</p>
<p>
	<strong>Sponsor:</strong> <a href="http://www.barebones.com/" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">BBEdit</a>: BBEdit is the leading professional-strength HTML and text editor for the Macintosh. A text power tool for everyone!</p>
